    "The Metaverse is filled with sound, and we think AI is playing a major role in audio management there.",
    "In the following, we illustrate in more detail some key concepts in NLP that can be used to create and enhance a Metaverse world.",
    "There are some of the challenges and problems associated with using AI for Avatar creation and customization in the Metaverse world:",
    "Quality of generated Avatars: One of the primary challenges with using AI for Avatar creation is generating high-quality Avatars.",
